Warnings
--------

. In order to compile this software you have to use a C++ revision equal or
  highter to C++14 (ISO/IEC 14882:2014).


Building
--------

. Build it:

    cmake .
    cmake --build_ .

  Library will be placed in "./lib" directory.


Documentation
-------------

. Generate documentation:

    doxygen Doxyfile
    
  Documentation will be placed in "./doc" directory.


Installation
------------

. Once compiled, to install the library you have to copy and paste in your 
  environment "./lib" and "./include" directories.
